        <mxCell id="-bMn6_9jcYxYQWy7xpfc-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Q. Design an Instagram like system:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;1. User login&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Service&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;2. Content&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Service&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;3. Feed&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Service&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;4. Follower&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Service&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;5. User engagement Service&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Implement a mechanism to restrict the user for posting a non-policy compliant post.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Optimize the dynamic feed generation for the users.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Highlight the use of Back-fill service.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A. Functional Requirements:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;1. User&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;should be able to register and login.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;2. User should be able to create post (text / image / videos).&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;3. Users&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;should be able to follow each other.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;4. User should be able to like or comment on the post.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;5. User&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;should be able to view the feed of post from users they follow.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;B. Non-Functional Requirements:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;1. Scalability: 1.5M DAU&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;2. Consistency and Availability:&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Here, in case of Social Media, Availability&amp;gt;&amp;gt;Consistency&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;3. Latency: 500ms to upload post&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;C. Core Entities:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;1. Users&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;2. Posts&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;3. Followers&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;4. Likes and Comments&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;5. Feeds&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;E. HLD:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace; font-size: 0px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;%3CmxGraphModel%3E%3Croot%3E%3CmxCell%20id%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3CmxCell%20id%3D%221%22%20parent%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3CmxCell%20id%3D%222%22%20parent%3D%221%22%20style%3D%22sketch%3D0%3BoutlineConnect%3D0%3BfontColor%3D%23232F3E%3BgradientColor%3Dnone%3BstrokeColor%3D%23232F3E%3BfillColor%3D%23ffffff%3Bdashed%3D0%3BverticalLabelPosition%3Dbottom%3BverticalAlign%3Dtop%3Balign%3Dcenter%3Bhtml%3D1%3BfontSize%3D12%3BfontStyle%3D0%3Baspect%3Dfixed%3Bshape%3Dmxgraph.aws4.resourceIcon%3BresIcon%3Dmxgraph.aws4.users%3B%22%20value%3D%22%22%20vertex%3D%221%22%3E%3CmxGeometry%20height%3D%2260%22%20width%3D%2260%22%20x%3D%22-750%22%20y%3D%223890%22%20as%3D%22geometry%22%2F%3E%3C%2FmxCell%3E%3C%2Froot%3E%3C%2FmxGraphModel%3E&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size